数据集| `platform.ultralytics.com/{username}/datasets/{slug}`| `platform.ultralytics.com/ultralytics/datasets/coco`  
项目| `platform.ultralytics.com/{username}/{project}`| `platform.ultralytics.com/ultralytics/yolo26`  
